{"tid":1578652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［停止fake news］重整國際文宣，重新集火真核彈","createTime":"2019-09-18T08:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T16:32:59.000Z","uid":82520,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"4881fe1a9aa9bbec37b10d1bcbcc4274c0a70c83","tid":1578652,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:19:54.000Z","msg":"如題，最近連登好多關於8.31死者/失蹤者嘅流言。又有新屋嶺義士被姦嘅講法。推測好多，真相欠奉。<br />\n<br />\n以上講法都有可能係真事。但係以外人角度嚟睇，幾聲慘叫可以叫人信有死人？一個醫生話會保護當時人就叫人信有女義士被強姦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲證據就算我信呀，你拎去國際戰線都冇人信啦。<br />\n<br />\n我地睇下琴日美國聽證會人地煲大啲咩。警暴，暴政，香港制度崩壞，chinazi對普世價值嘅打壓。點解呢啲可以放去大枱面？全部有證有據，對其他人亦有切身影響。police brutality, chinazi 呢啲就係我地目前要煲大嘅野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爆眼，新屋嶺私刑證言，扮示威者衝擊，水炮車射記者，濫捕，警黑等等。呢啲黑警完全冇得兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一星期重溫一次好過你post rumors<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，未完全證實嘅野唔係唔理，但唔好急於放到國際層面。就好似831太子封站咁，呢單一直有議員跟緊，真相會愈辨愈明。呢啲我地就要做多啲本地文宣，推番press con 啲post 上熱門！我相信條timeline咁複雜，件事又咁多版本，連香港人都唔完全了解始末。<br />\n<br />\n講到尾，比番啲建議大家，你可能已經聽過好多次，但真係要做出嚟<br />\n<br />\n1.）善用不推文回覆<br />\n推文好簡單，推之前諗下係咪好真係信得過，唔好好似藍絲咁人講乜信乜<br />\n<br />\n2.）推番正視聽嘅post<br />\n議員presscon，民記，行動post。<br />\n<br />\n3.）Twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家真係要開始用Twitter，國際文宣組一直有出英文文宣，唔好白費人心機。<br />\npost文有片/圖加上簡略英文解釋，再加個hashtag推上trending<br />\n<br />\n我地唔輸得，國際戰線係場運動樽頸嘅突破點。唔好睇小和理非鍵戰文宣，每人行一步，就係好撚多步。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"7fefd006a1232a24b055b9989f8bf304b6dc2338","tid":1578652,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:20:39.000Z","msg":"少長，希望大家認真睇睇，有建議隨時歡迎"},{"pid":"7b4e77afb8e8960c9950a083d5fedf55a3863a4f","tid":1578652,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:20:52.000Z","msg":"推 2"},{"pid":"16bf4f38eb65b10f620163801ee81b75deb19915","tid":1578652,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:25:48.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"eb4cb84c8bde360602124f1cccfdf859f602b685","tid":1578652,"uid":306180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:27:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔知推咩tweet好？<br />\n有人幫你整理埋啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\ntwitter共識channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87EvjycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=55e02724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a>"},{"pid":"faea1841b7dd0b2795f675c1872076ec1442bddb","tid":1578652,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:29:42.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"aecc183a0ccb7f4741e82eaeb3894825f758ab05","tid":1578652,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"8ab76a2835ad2b94ba9b029a121c2435fa08cab2","tid":1578652,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"ru"},{"pid":"bfc75f01cf3cfa0f2c98d1805385e4f7e13be7a9","tid":1578652,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:38:15.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"e1398597431530e212fdc8b2db343d5d25121e26","tid":1578652,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:39:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5401087ad89e2ec27efea1c77719318ff8a1f7b","tid":1578652,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:47:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f536256af68be586f0b4e182572e309bdaf62922","tid":1578652,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:47:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"69e82dd7513494a2d2c86bbb63267b9cb84c13a9","tid":1578652,"uid":100714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"87016a5c4abc4edbd4c188080560986246808809","tid":1578652,"uid":278092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f05fae2fe80944789553ae5d35d793c22f0722","tid":1578652,"uid":86724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:50:42.000Z","msg":"岩岩出左個post都係講類似嘅野<br />\n<br />\n各位唔好再傳fake news，未證實嘅寫返未FC！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1578436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1578436</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n連登呢排d重要post比fake news洗走哂<br />\n要推測討論唔係唔得，但可以集合返一個post去講<br />\n依家洗走哂重要post，唉<br />\n我見都有唔少巴打講過呢個問題，但個個post都推唔上熱門<br />\n依家熱門有好多何妖，真係太多，仲有警犬出軌呢類，根本對示威都無咩用⋯<br />\n<br />\n幫你推"},{"pid":"ce16b6193e5671a06483d1ff7b0dd016c2c44ad0","tid":1578652,"uid":86724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"國際文宣都好撚重要！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n除左twitter都可以玩下YouTube <br />\n依家YouTube 好多5毛片，一搵721 炮台山呢d就已經5毛片<br />\n外國人想fact check都難<br />\n大家都可以幫手Upload d片上YouTube，方便人地fc同埋自己人澄清用<br />\n另外，YouTube 上面有利我地嘅片都好少views，大家都可以幫手刷下、留言<br />\n<br />\n我地要更多國家幫手啊！要更多外國人知咩事！<br />\n國際文宣加油！"},{"pid":"1cccd1101ac46b968e0fc94a49a7be6cac89e78a","tid":1578652,"uid":86724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:57:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b2ff17424469c97234119fd57307d447d1fafb9","tid":1578652,"uid":86724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:57:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9e7bd65b54b67496e3d4dd1f46b66b6bba71e03","tid":1578652,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:58:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5ba557a9b80f37d3e1d8721f4423e0df136e15a6","tid":1578652,"uid":1581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:58:22.000Z","msg":"我地要集中做實事搞遊行<br />\n<br />\n另外集中番證據確實既警暴同警黑勾結"},{"pid":"835ac3bc1336e23ce993a023861407c8ebf21fd7","tid":1578652,"uid":192242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:00:00.000Z","msg":"［港女國際線］求五大訴求翻譯版！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"51f3e737accee967892ea28cac7180a88252e65e","tid":1578652,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:00:23.000Z","msg":"可以幫手查,但係唔好單單都話核彈要推上國際"},{"pid":"1a43a116f81159b23b80ae88163a774a2a103067","tid":1578652,"uid":60562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:01:58.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n<br />\n點解連登而家咩都話核蛋同咁多陰謀論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577876</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"691f448fcd7ea2469a711849c1444d1f8dc029d8","tid":1578652,"uid":108997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:02:10.000Z","msg":"善用不推文功能"},{"pid":"96be570aad5fbb8fa09e301dfcaeff204e2481d2","tid":1578652,"uid":86724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:08:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"378321dd740987adfb43cd462e37a5ad41b87093","tid":1578652,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8296ec36ea91a29d6a265c6bc45b67df3806f88e","tid":1578652,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88a362c8efaf66e92bb652c908c1abb6072fcf3","tid":1578652,"uid":129883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29bd8392aff697c8cbc1945d7342def2314ca915","tid":1578652,"uid":314549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e7zK5j8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe7zK5j8.jpg&h=0d61435b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9791120565091a6fcd4dfa37e969357509a5099d","tid":1578652,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"優先搞有證據嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678a677c21402c7fc350a92c06853cb6daadea22","tid":1578652,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:13:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcb8c86ae2528ac073bfe6d8e4e4d9562bd09e42","tid":1578652,"uid":249586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:14:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0e3aa787e8069dc20f337bcb872c623b3376b7","tid":1578652,"uid":163630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:16:22.000Z","msg":"係呀,國際政府都要睇當地民意, 如果民意唔支持, 國際政府想出手都唔係咁易, 所以我地唔好俾民意逆轉, 大家繼續努力!"},{"pid":"bd92af6e05ab2aa09d9412bb6457cad7cafa33f0","tid":1578652,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:21:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"31fbc19c998b504fb706b775e70580dada3f0e07","tid":1578652,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:23:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b019e8ed3975360b8596704cd17b3bfc9d1e17a","tid":1578652,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:23:26.000Z","msg":"【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！快閃式萬國「民主」旗號召世界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eccnjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eccnjS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n由於香港身為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>東道主</strong></span></span>倘若因為任何原因而令到遊行人數小得難睇, 是不理想的！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我寧願<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>10.1國殤</strong></span>打到拆天就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然大家請記著呢日唔是End-game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由美帝反共眾議員可以見到場戰爭並非一朝一夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失去所有勇武運動將難以持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講到星期日9.29是全球性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單靠香港人文宣團隊twitter retweet比當地人是難以收到巨大宣傳效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唯有無比juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方法去呼喚他國人民, 同埋件事夠juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國媒體先會幫你免費頭版</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！<br />\n集合時間：1930~2000<br />\n遊行時間：2000~終點和平散去 (預計9點前行到遮打即龍頭散去)<br />\n舉行日期：9月23日至9月27日晚上快閃式遊行<br />\n遊行路線：修頓球場 至 遮打花園<br />\n注意事項：遊行完就即時由中環遮打盡快散去！不起衝突！人小就行行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣著：遊行時黑色, 前往及離開時非黑色<br />\n快閃遊行目的：號召全球「反共」聯軍同時響應9.29大遊行, 盡可能與香港同步舉行！</strong></span><br />\n利申：是次遊行屬自發性質, 沒有不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到反共你走去申請唔好傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我主張每晚均可見到頭60名民主國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要有60位手足舉60支旗個畫面已經夠晒Juicy<br />\n首先你話該國家一直龜縮有咩撚用,舉嚟把撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是9.29反共大遊行號召目標是各國人民,<br />\n如果我地真是連續一星期舉民主國家國旗, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>當地右翼會相當自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>,<br />\n同埋每晚我地可以twitter開放檢討比各國人民知道其國旗在香港揚起以打倒中共</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b7bd6344ab237e30e1c28f73a7ec8240c073b435","tid":1578652,"uid":50437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09eaf916e9dc9852aec4ea1f2add20f7bb6bba23","tid":1578652,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f85613fb6399aaedf13ffcb1be58c4584c84400","tid":1578652,"uid":222771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:27:26.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5d31479d7de05afa5b29dc9355a0ed3a232622f2","tid":1578652,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:27:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abc931e13e98e6ca14a4f88570dc6522cd10e4a9","tid":1578652,"uid":72730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:29:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中火力講香港係全球民主最前線</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"32463c7ad651d19fbf9806aec09c3cb2c22ab62b","tid":1578652,"uid":311452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:32:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aafdbcc8f997cd5fb9838e60ba1e0294553b0547","tid":1578652,"uid":138144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"Bump"},{"pid":"0ea5fe4a030bc88fa376912e5314c1bc5b482cca","tid":1578652,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:33:08.000Z","msg":"善用 我傾向相信有死到人"},{"pid":"1d5d10f3e241f4fea528de5160c300ae431b150a","tid":1578652,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:33:20.000Z","msg":"【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！快閃式萬國「民主」旗號召世界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eccnjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eccnjS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n由於香港身為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-si